title: Stacey Q - Better Than Heaven [1986]
description:
Stacey Q - Better Than Heaven [1986]

While she now languishes in the bin known as 'one-hit wonder', Stacey Q actually had a whole album side that was worth spilling the beans, that being Side A of Better Than Heaven. Typical mid-80's techno, yes, but well-written, well-performed, well-produced. "Two Of Hearts" was a good one, of course, but falls short of better dishes such as "Better Than Heaven" and "Don't Let Me Down". "We Connect" and "Insecurity" were also rather goodish, and the voice just oozes sexuality. 

Stacey Q - vocals 
music performed by SSQ (no credits given beyond the names): 
Skip Hahn 
Karl Moet 
Rich West 
Jon St. James 
Produced by Jon St. James
